         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translations</head>
            <div type="translation" source="#jmr-jbwp-rgg2003" xml:lang="en"><p>Theodotos the bishop lies here</p></div>
            </div>
       
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>This is the only bishop's tomb that has so far been identified in Cyrenaica. Theodotos was presumably another of the rural bishops for which the provinces of Libya Superior and Libya Inferior are well-known;
               they are of course a natural development in an area where the number of cities
             was small and the rural territory large.</p>
         </div>
         
